    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">This ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a majestic design with a beautiful bald eagle overlaid with the American Flag, making this a great patriotic gift for men. The eagle is also depicted on the handle of the blade, and the pommel is shaped like an eagle’s head, perfect for any knife enthusiast’s collection. The knife is designed for display but also features an ergonomic handle that will keep the blade from slipping during use. Ergonomic handles are great for hunters and those who rely on their blades being easy and comfortable to use in the field</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor American Flag Eagle Fixed Blade Hunting Knife Patriotic Gift 3 Style</h2>\n  <p>This ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a majestic design with a beautiful bald eagle overlaid with the American Flag, making this a great patriotic gift for men. The eagle is also depicted on the handle of the blade, and the pommel is shaped like an eagle’s head, perfect for any knife enthusiast’s collection.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>PATRIOTIC KNIFE GIFT - This ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a majestic design with a beautiful bald eagle overlaid with the American Flag, making this a great patriotic gift for men. The eagle is also depicted on the handle of the blade, and the pommel is shaped like an eagle’s head, perfect for any knife enthusiast’s collection.</li>\n    <li>ERGONOMIC HANDLE - The knife is designed for display, but also features an ergonomic handle that will keep the blade from slipping during use. Ergonomic handles are great for hunters and those who rely on their blades being easy and comfortable to use in the field.</li>\n    <li>STRAIGHT-BACK BLADE - In addition to being a great collector’s item, the ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a straight-back blade that is particularly popular for survival-style knives because it is excellent for slicing since the majority of the blade is simple to maintain along a cut line. They are also easy to sharpen since they only feature a single curve along the front.</li>\n    <li>IDEAL SIZE FOR DISPLAY - Each knife measures 13.5” in length, making it the perfect size for a knife display case or collection shelf. The stainless steel blade itself features a Damascus steel design that gives the knife a classic Damascus hunting knife look.</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Material:</strong> stainless steel that won’t rust; Colors: American flag/eagle, assorted; Dimensions: 13.5” overall length; Plastic sheath included; Designed for display</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/71997/UuOumSDcwyswDSwZJQI99YByomsk75-metaYW1lYWdfZGFnZ2VyX3BhcmVudC5qcGc=-.jpg\" alt=\"This ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a majestic design with a beautiful bald eagle overlaid with the American Flag, making this a great patriotic\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> AMEAGBLD1</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058480125</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Large</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The knife is designed for display but also features an ergonomic handle that will keep the blade from slipping during use. Ergonomic handles are great for hunters and those who rely on their blades being easy and comfortable to use in the field.</p>\n  <p>In addition to being a great collector’s item, the ASR Outdoor hunting knife features a straight-back blade that is particularly popular for survival-style knives because it is excellent for slicing since the majority of the blade is simple to maintain along a cut line. They are also easy to sharpen since they only feature a single curve along the front.</p>\n  <p>Each knife measures 13.5” in length, making it the perfect size for a knife display case or collection shelf. The stainless steel blade itself features a Damascus steel design that gives the knife a classic Damascus hunting knife look. Make sure to grab one of these knives for a gift or for your own collection!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
